high_descs: Go straight and then right into the first path, heading straight down to the fridge.
Pick up the knife from the fridge.
Turn around and go straight ahead to the living room, stopping and turning right to the microwave on the table.
Slice the potato that is in front of the microwave.
Look down to the left side of the table.
Place the knife down to the left of the microwave.
Look back to the sliced up potato.
Pick up one potato slice.
Return to the fridge you got the knife from.
Place the potato slice in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn around and walk ahead, stopping at the sink on the right.
Place the potato slice into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cool a potato slice in a fridge and place it in a sink.

high_descs: Walk along the wall on the right all the way to a fridge.
Take a knife out of the fridge.
Turn around and walk alongside the left wall, but when you pass it, turn right and go to a sidetable with a microwave.
Cut a potato on the table with the knife.
Stand with your back to the wall and the sidetable on your right.
Place the knife on the sidetable.
Move back in front of the sidetable.
Pick up a potato slice from the sidetable.
Move back to the fridge.
Put the potato slice in the fridge, let it cool for a while, then take it out.
Turn around, follow the sink table on your left, and walk to the other side of it to face the sink.
Put the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled potato slice in the kitchen sink.
